<body>
    <h1>Task 13- RAD</h1>
    <div class=3D"Section1">
        <h1 local-id=3D"d3e43b598f42" id=3D"Task13-RAD-1.Introduction">1. I=
ntroduction</h1>
<h2 local-id=3D"8714cca02b6d" id=3D"Task13-RAD-1.1Purpose">1.1 Purpose</h2>
<p local-id=3D"ba4fdf015445">The purpose of this document is to describe th=
e requirements for developing a Linux shell script that automatically deplo=
ys an observability stack on an AWS EC2 instance.</p>
<p local-id=3D"0c85355dfb9b">The observability stack includes:</p>
<ul>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"b9093687f6bb">Prometheus for metrics collection</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"59b948b59e50">Grafana Loki for centralized log storage</p></=
li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"dd1f1acdafd2">Grafana Mimir for scalable metrics storage</p>=
</li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"3950c73fa5cb">Grafana for visualization and monitoring dashb=
oards</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"40be8a19d47a">The intended audience for this document includ=
es:</p>
<ul>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"e28191603810">DevOps Engineers</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"2a8e78ca09dd">Cloud Engineers</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"c541e99efab2">System Administrators</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"e6f9185c87ca">Technical Reviewers</p></li>
</ul>
<hr>
<h2 local-id=3D"c28d951fdf96" id=3D"Task13-RAD-1.2Scope">1.2 Scope</h2>
<p local-id=3D"16ade509392e">The scope of the project includes:</p>
<ul>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"6a9571ce7104">Deploying the observability stack on an AWS EC=
2 instance</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"35234e48a822">Automating the installation and configuration =
using a Linux shell script</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"ea3b909bef4f">Ensuring that all services start automatically=
 and are accessible after deployment</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"69ef172e82a7">The project includes:</p>
<ul>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"19567ab0a277">Installation of required dependencies</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"f4ec4f806529">Configuration of Prometheus, Loki, Mimir, and =
Grafana</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"c3ee350b6727">Creation of system services for automatic star=
tup</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"8f02b855ba86">Basic validation of services</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"6e3ca913d45e">The project does <strong>not include</strong>:=
</p>
<ul>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"3650d66aba43">Production-scale clustering</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"9c450f0c098b">High availability deployment</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"3c62c5451f92">Advanced alerting or complex dashboards</p></l=
i>
</ul>
<hr>
<h2 local-id=3D"9123ab887519" id=3D"Task13-RAD-1.3Definitions,Acronyms,andA=
bbreviations">1.3 Definitions, Acronyms, and Abbreviations</h2>
<div class=3D"table-wrap">
<table data-table-width=3D"1800" data-layout=3D"default" data-local-id=3D"b=
bfa49ab-b995-455d-a16c-8b569e384b24" class=3D"confluenceTable">
<tbody>
<tr>
<th class=3D"confluenceTh">
<p local-id=3D"084572050897">Term</p></th>
<th class=3D"confluenceTh">
<p local-id=3D"f5c08cf21c4a">Description</p></th>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"f44e0c891b0c">EC2</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"7becc691c4df">Elastic Compute Cloud virtual server in AWS</p=
></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"7eebebc6dccb">DevOps</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"b637e5b8a571">Development and operations practices for autom=
ation</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"09697c161d1b">Observability</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"e51c97abb961">Ability to monitor system health using metrics=
, logs, and traces</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"2095ee27d18c">Metrics</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"c19a31975290">Numerical measurements representing system per=
formance</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"19b44a92cf20">Logs</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"22fbb24ca985">Recorded events generated by system applicatio=
ns</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"3f1325c8037c">Dashboard</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"9420e2d35c46">Visual interface used to monitor metrics</p></=
td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</div>
<hr>
<h2 local-id=3D"f4e6c733cfcc" id=3D"Task13-RAD-1.4References">1.4 Reference=
s</h2>
<p local-id=3D"565a9c0a36ce">AWS Documentation<br><a href=3D"https://docs.a=
ws.amazon.com/" class=3D"external-link" rel=3D"nofollow">https://docs.aws.a=
mazon.com/</a></p>
<p local-id=3D"248eb47a5c87">Prometheus Documentation<br><a href=3D"https:/=
/prometheus.io/docs/" data-card-appearance=3D"inline" class=3D"external-lin=
k" rel=3D"nofollow">https://prometheus.io/docs/</a></p>
<p local-id=3D"b4ffce546a54">Grafana Documentation<br><a href=3D"https://gr=
afana.com/docs/?utm_source=3Dchatgpt.com" class=3D"external-link" rel=3D"no=
follow">https://grafana.com/docs/</a></p>
<p local-id=3D"307d2bfce180">Loki Documentation<br><a href=3D"https://grafa=
na.com/docs/loki/" data-card-appearance=3D"inline" class=3D"external-link" =
rel=3D"nofollow">https://grafana.com/docs/loki/</a></p>
<p local-id=3D"34e7db5ad398">Mimir Documentation<br><a href=3D"https://graf=
ana.com/docs/mimir/" data-card-appearance=3D"inline" class=3D"external-link=
" rel=3D"nofollow">https://grafana.com/docs/mimir/</a></p>
<hr>
<h2 local-id=3D"e58e2beeb8e9" id=3D"Task13-RAD-1.5Overview">1.5 Overview</h=
2>
<p local-id=3D"451a523b67d4">This document provides:</p>
<ul>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"51596e1b52aa">Project objectives and business context</p></l=
i>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"c2947a33c05e">Functional requirements with use cases</p></li=
>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"00d9d70f2b9e">Non-functional requirements</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"66de8722814e">Risk analysis</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"fdc2bfceec07">Project assumptions and dependencies</p></li>
</ul>
<hr>
<h1 local-id=3D"5e6b5f3868aa" id=3D"Task13-RAD-2.ProjectOverview">2. Projec=
t Overview</h1>
<h2 local-id=3D"996b72b70be5" id=3D"Task13-RAD-2.1ProjectObjectives">2.1 Pr=
oject Objectives</h2>
<p local-id=3D"5309397dd368">The main objective of the project is to create=
 a reusable Linux shell script that automatically deploys an observability =
stack on AWS EC2.</p>
<p local-id=3D"5ae716648583">The deployment should ensure:</p>
<ul>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"4bdcb651dad9">Automated installation of monitoring tools</p>=
</li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"b978ea6f86df">Simplified setup for new environments</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"f6c6276afdda">Consistent configuration across deployments</p=
></li>
</ul>
<hr>
<h2 local-id=3D"dcbb30942d90" id=3D"Task13-RAD-2.2BusinessGoals">2.2 Busine=
ss Goals</h2>
<p local-id=3D"470f83f15a3b">The business goals of the project include:</p>
<ul>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"5f35f570b59c">Reducing manual setup time for monitoring syst=
ems</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"a47a14e8ba33">Ensuring consistent observability environments=
 across infrastructure</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"5db56ab68afb">Improving system monitoring capabilities</p></=
li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"ee8b74a5b92f">Enabling faster troubleshooting through centra=
lized logging and metrics</p></li>
</ul>
<hr>
<h2 local-id=3D"b695d7abcf44" id=3D"Task13-RAD-2.3Background">2.3 Backgroun=
d</h2>
<p local-id=3D"2a23e60fb2b4">Modern cloud infrastructures require continuou=
s monitoring and log analysis to maintain system reliability.</p>
<p local-id=3D"fb21fe3358c9">Manual deployment of monitoring tools often le=
ads to:</p>
<ul>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"3383fafe1893">Configuration errors</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"02ec52c89ed7">Time-consuming setup processes</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"05231174d146">Inconsistent monitoring environments</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"b5341e3f706b">Automating the deployment process using script=
s allows organizations to quickly provision monitoring infrastructure acros=
s environments.</p>
<hr>
<h2 local-id=3D"c96808974e75" id=3D"Task13-RAD-2.4Constraints">2.4 Constrai=
nts</h2>
<p local-id=3D"ee2d5558a322">The project has the following constraints:</p>
<ul>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"d4cf51b774c0">Deployment must run on a single EC2 instance</=
p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"56a3e508a903">The script must work on a fresh Linux environm=
ent</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"abba43673728">The solution must be implemented using shell s=
cripting</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"ccdb2b509255">The implementation must be completed within th=
e project time limit</p></li>
</ul>
<hr>
<h1 local-id=3D"465a10580d67" id=3D"Task13-RAD-3.FunctionalRequirements">3.=
 Functional Requirements</h1>
<h2 local-id=3D"dd583c62c9ea" id=3D"Task13-RAD-3.1UseCaseDiagram">3.1 Use C=
ase Diagram</h2>
<p local-id=3D"c8bbdc34c721">Actors:</p>
<ul>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"42423c2511b6">DevOps Engineer</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"b57a3314d2ff">System Administrator</p></li>
</ul><span class=3D"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper c=
onfluence-embedded-manual-size"><img class=3D"confluence-embedded-image ima=
ge-center" alt=3D"Untitled Diagram.drawio (16)-20260312-084321.png" width=
=3D"468" loading=3D"lazy" src=3D"084ba0abe4201bff0964c25e1ec020e9b5d084e6be=
bdb8b07026a2abbad9a442" data-image-src=3D"https://iamops.atlassian.net/wiki=
/download/attachments/1856208914/Untitled%20Diagram.drawio%20(16)-20260312-=
084321.png?version=3D1&amp;modificationDate=3D1773340410933&amp;cacheVersio=
n=3D1&amp;api=3Dv2" data-height=3D"821" data-width=3D"1031" data-unresolved=
-comment-count=3D"0" data-linked-resource-id=3D"1858174977" data-linked-res=
ource-version=3D"1" data-linked-resource-type=3D"attachment" data-linked-re=
source-default-alias=3D"Untitled Diagram.drawio (16)-20260312-084321.png" d=
ata-base-url=3D"https://iamops.atlassian.net/wiki" data-linked-resource-con=
tent-type=3D"image/png" data-linked-resource-container-id=3D"1856208914" da=
ta-linked-resource-container-version=3D"3" data-media-id=3D"732dac1e-1963-4=
243-9625-4421cd97f7e2" data-media-type=3D"file" height=3D"372"></span>
<p local-id=3D"d79b1d87cfa7">System:</p>
<p local-id=3D"4b00bdc67737">Automated Observability Deployment Script</p>
<p local-id=3D"4b5e409025c7">Main interactions include:</p>
<ul>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"57ee86a29c77">Launch EC2 instance</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"a299d1974877">Execute deployment script</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"6c4df74167d2">Install monitoring components</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"d30f33f84f06">Start system services</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"177c425b6cfd">Access monitoring dashboards</p></li>
</ul>
<hr>
<h1 local-id=3D"1a3cb2b7e22d" id=3D"Task13-RAD-3.2UseCases">3.2 Use Cases</=
h1>
<hr>
<h1 local-id=3D"5bf62d8a4fc7" id=3D"Task13-RAD-3.2.1UseCase1:PrepareEC2Inst=
ance">3.2.1 Use Case 1: Prepare EC2 Instance</h1>
<p local-id=3D"a842fc00ec4a">Description<br>
Provision an EC2 instance that will host the observability stack.</p>
<p local-id=3D"759909e41efb">Actors<br>
DevOps Engineer</p>
<p local-id=3D"c4568f021c98">Preconditions</p>
<ul>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"c73dab4c3464">AWS account access available</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"6a956a704803">EC2 permissions configured</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"5ec0ddf71505">Postconditions</p>
<ul>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"751d4d66d2e0">EC2 instance ready for deployment</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"a39d13adcc39">Flow of Events</p>
<ol start=3D"1">
<li>
<p local-id=3D"df5e2ee69174">DevOps engineer launches EC2 instance</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"f020435d4527">Required security groups are configured</p></l=
i>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"31fff20354a3">Instance is accessed via SSH</p></li>
</ol>
<p local-id=3D"86014eb1c9b7">Alternative Flow</p>
<p local-id=3D"d30a77e5c95e">Incorrect security group configuration prevent=
s service access.</p>
<hr>
<h1 local-id=3D"448b93292dd3" id=3D"Task13-RAD-3.2.2UseCase2:ExecuteDeploym=
entScript">3.2.2 Use Case 2: Execute Deployment Script</h1>
<p local-id=3D"e03ffa274d3d">Description<br>
Run the deployment script to automate installation of observability tools.<=
/p>
<p local-id=3D"ab5df75b176d">Actors<br>
DevOps Engineer</p>
<p local-id=3D"a4284d959efd">Preconditions</p>
<ul>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"deaab7051c14">EC2 instance accessible via SSH</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"a31e5eaf05d2">Deployment script available</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"7d882d632f6c">Postconditions</p>
<ul>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"0991d21f5b6e">Installation process begins</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"057a9f849728">Flow of Events</p>
<ol start=3D"1">
<li>
<p local-id=3D"c338c903bab9">User uploads deployment script to EC2</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"08673d2f236c">Script is given execution permission</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"5ad8a3f72d64">Script execution begins</p></li>
</ol>
<p local-id=3D"8968423c7350">Alternative Flow</p>
<p local-id=3D"e0a045803dff">Script fails due to missing dependencies.</p>
<hr>
<h1 local-id=3D"4e31f652faae" id=3D"Task13-RAD-3.2.3UseCase3:InstallDepende=
ncies">3.2.3 Use Case 3: Install Dependencies</h1>
<p local-id=3D"43bc5da23629">Description<br>
Install required packages needed for the monitoring stack.</p>
<p local-id=3D"54f4b8f86138">Actors<br>
Deployment Script</p>
<p local-id=3D"10c273f527a1">Preconditions</p>
<ul>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"27779ddf0e9f">Script execution started</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"8781ea831423">Postconditions</p>
<ul>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"c42e8bf53440">Required dependencies installed</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"4dffcd959f81">Flow of Events</p>
<ol start=3D"1">
<li>
<p local-id=3D"95873f3d6159">Script updates system packages</p></li>
<li>
