<h1 local-id=3D"e070e7496a6d" id=3D"Task13-RAD-4.Non-FunctionalRequirements=
">4. Non-Functional Requirements</h1>
<h2 local-id=3D"47cde80d3570" id=3D"Task13-RAD-4.1PerformanceRequirements">=
4.1 Performance Requirements</h2>
<p local-id=3D"70cbea197939">The deployment script should complete executio=
n within a reasonable time frame and should not significantly impact system=
 performance during installation.</p>
<hr>
<h2 local-id=3D"8d3188af0225" id=3D"Task13-RAD-4.2SecurityRequirements">4.2=
 Security Requirements</h2>
<p local-id=3D"8d8c4d1b5f91">System services should run under dedicated use=
rs to minimize security risks.</p>
<p local-id=3D"5d1f4ceb9907">Access to monitoring dashboards should be rest=
ricted through proper authentication mechanisms.</p>
<hr>
<h2 local-id=3D"574392fdabc0" id=3D"Task13-RAD-4.3UsabilityRequirements">4.=
3 Usability Requirements</h2>
<p local-id=3D"d8942ef7369a">The deployment script should be easy to execut=
e and should require minimal user interaction.</p>
<p local-id=3D"9225b4c4ef56">Clear comments should be included to improve r=
eadability and understanding.</p>
<hr>
<h2 local-id=3D"4e2a583795fa" id=3D"Task13-RAD-4.4ReliabilityRequirements">=
4.4 Reliability Requirements</h2>
<p local-id=3D"69143346d64f">All deployed services should automatically res=
tart after system reboot to maintain continuous monitoring functionality.</=
p>
<hr>
<h2 local-id=3D"8c14fc60980a" id=3D"Task13-RAD-4.5ComplianceRequirements">4=
.5 Compliance Requirements</h2>
<p local-id=3D"559b5cee1194">The deployment process should follow best prac=
tices for cloud infrastructure management and system monitoring.</p>
<hr>
<h1 local-id=3D"a31b660c8ac1" id=3D"Task13-RAD-5.AssumptionsandDependencies=
">5. Assumptions and Dependencies</h1>
<h2 local-id=3D"4b2527f0d895" id=3D"Task13-RAD-5.1Assumptions">5.1 Assumpti=
ons</h2>
<p local-id=3D"970dbf2a726d">The EC2 instance has internet access for downl=
oading packages.</p>
<p local-id=3D"182ca4a8b20b">The deployment script will be executed by a us=
er with administrative privileges.</p>
<hr>
<h2 local-id=3D"dc704883c4b4" id=3D"Task13-RAD-5.2Dependencies">5.2 Depende=
ncies</h2>
<p local-id=3D"f148b759993c">The project depends on:</p>
<ul>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"a8b54724f197">AWS EC2 infrastructure</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"183f44a4a24d">Internet connectivity</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"617bd0821247">Linux operating system</p></li>
</ul>
<hr>
<h1 local-id=3D"5abf832ea165" id=3D"Task13-RAD-6.RiskAnalysis">6. Risk Anal=
ysis</h1>
<h2 local-id=3D"518cc6cc39a5" id=3D"Task13-RAD-6.1RiskIdentification">6.1 R=
isk Identification</h2>
<div class=3D"table-wrap">
<table data-table-width=3D"1800" data-layout=3D"default" data-local-id=3D"b=
97b5164-882d-4a4b-82e8-23df3ab769e4" class=3D"confluenceTable">
<tbody>
<tr>
<th class=3D"confluenceTh">
<p local-id=3D"b00ee76bbf1e">Risk</p></th>
<th class=3D"confluenceTh">
<p local-id=3D"0b49c0ad0b75">Description</p></th>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"38e1a5c8a663">Network connectivity issues</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"cad004b0dd14">Packages cannot be downloaded</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"e3317c729322">Incorrect configuration</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"7b5e8cba4d41">Services may fail to start</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"6a2ad144ee2d">Port conflicts</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"99ff74243ebb">Monitoring tools cannot bind to ports</p></td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</div>
<hr>
<h2 local-id=3D"e418886c207e" id=3D"Task13-RAD-6.2RiskMitigation">6.2 Risk =
Mitigation</h2>
<div class=3D"table-wrap">
<table data-table-width=3D"1800" data-layout=3D"default" data-local-id=3D"e=
a455dcc-009b-410a-8110-d1608bd819bf" class=3D"confluenceTable">
<tbody>
<tr>
<th class=3D"confluenceTh">
<p local-id=3D"86b981675968">Risk</p></th>
<th class=3D"confluenceTh">
<p local-id=3D"46e6ef946db6">Mitigation</p></th>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"cbcb1b246209">Network issues</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"7c4b6d5d7466">Verify connectivity before execution</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"ad874adaaa0e">Configuration errors</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"cb0b3ee3c426">Use tested configuration files</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"c3a878e7b249">Port conflicts</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"15fe5abe66fe">Validate service ports before deployment</p></=
td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</div>
<hr>
